1
00:00:14,725 --> 00:00:18,487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

2
00:00:18,562 --> 00:00:22,162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

3
00:00:22,287 --> 00:00:25,437
♪Your “same here” carries
a touch of resolve♪

4
00:00:25,862 --> 00:00:29,412
♪Pack my bags,
we can set off right now♪

5
00:00:29,637 --> 00:00:33,112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

6
00:00:33,250 --> 00:00:36,712
♪The journey itself is what truly matters
before the destination♪

7
00:00:36,787 --> 00:00:40,975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

8
00:00:41,025 --> 00:00:42,612
♪Connect♪

9
00:00:42,625 --> 00:00:43,275
♪Let's go!♪

10
00:00:43,612 --> 00:00:47,137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

11
00:00:47,237 --> 00:00:50,675
♪Today, no dwelling on
negative emotions♪

12
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:53,450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

13
00:00:53,450 --> 00:00:55,262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

14
00:00:55,262 --> 00:00:58,199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

15
00:00:59,075 --> 00:01:02,375
=Love in A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

16
00:01:02,675 --> 00:01:06,237
=Episode 22=

17
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:10,120
Dear, stand properly.

18
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:12,640
Strand straight.

19
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,120
Your hands.

20
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:15,160
Your arms.

21
00:01:15,240 --> 00:01:16,200
Lift them.

22
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:18,360
That's too high. Lower them.

23
00:01:18,440 --> 00:01:20,520
Wait, your expression isn't right.

24
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:22,520
Like this.

25
00:01:23,320 --> 00:01:24,520
Put them down.

26
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:28,400
Like this.

27
00:01:30,720 --> 00:01:32,920
I've stood for two hours.

28
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:33,987
I'm exhausted.

29
00:01:33,987 --> 00:01:35,347
No, I can't do this anymore.

30
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:38,440
Is it really that tiring?

31
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:41,720
Hey.

32
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:43,720
Let me see what my wife has drawn.

33
00:01:43,720 --> 00:01:45,680
Don't look.

34
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,840
This isn't me, is it?

35
00:01:47,960 --> 00:01:49,760
Who is this supposed to be?

36
00:01:49,770 --> 00:01:51,230
Do you have someone else in your heart?

37
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:52,320
I'm not telling you.

38
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:55,280
This is a gorgeous guy I like.

39
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:57,360
Dear.

40
00:01:58,600 --> 00:01:59,160
Oh.

41
00:02:00,240 --> 00:02:01,760
Qi, what brings you here?

42
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,120
Why can't I come?

43
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,720
I came to check up on you.

44
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:05,880
Great.

45
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:07,480
I wish you could stay at the company
with me every day.

46
00:02:08,760 --> 00:02:09,120
Well.

47
00:02:10,040 --> 00:02:10,720
This is...

48
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:13,600
This is Qingbai I told you about.

49
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:23,560
Hello?

50
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:25,280
I'm in Shenzhen for a meeting.

51
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:27,440
Mm.

52
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:28,560
Bye.

53
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:37,240
Shen Qi is about to give birth, right?

54
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,600
The due date is next month.

55
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,800
You always say

56
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:47,240
I've changed.

57
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:49,680
But what you don't know is

58
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:52,840
that last summer,

59
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:55,720
the one who came back from Spain

60
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:56,920
wasn't Lu Zhu.

61
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,280
It was me,

62
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:02,520
Sun.

63
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:14,320
When I first learned about this,

64
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:17,320
I hated Mom.

65
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:20,040
I hated her for venting all the hatred
she felt toward you

66
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,320
on me.

67
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:25,520
I hated her for keeping Zhu

68
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,680
instead of me.

69
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,280
I hated

70
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:33,480
that no one had truly loved me
since birth.

71
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:37,240
I was like a sacrifice for your love.

72
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:40,720
When your marriage died,

73
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,760
you buried me with it.

74
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,560
But later,

75
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,000
I met Zhu.

76
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,840
She came to Spain to find me.

77
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:04,800
In just one month,

78
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,680
she made up for the 18 years I had lost.

79
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:14,320
She was even better
than the Lu family's daughter

80
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:16,880
you all talk about.

81
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,720
Gentle,

82
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,240
kind,

83
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,080
and strong.

84
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,640
She told me

85
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:33,000
not to blame you and Mom.

86
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:39,440
She told me everything

87
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:41,520
about what happened between you two.

88
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,640
She also said

89
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,960
that whenever Mom had nightmares,

90
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,880
she cried out my name.

91
00:04:55,612 --> 00:04:57,412
So she did love me.

92
00:04:58,880 --> 00:05:00,440
She loved me.

93
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,360
But what about you?

94
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:09,240
Did you love the woman

95
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:13,080
who bore your children for you?

96
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,520
Dad,

97
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:19,040
have you ever regretted it?

98
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:25,440
Everything you said...

99
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,120
Was everything you said all true?

100
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:29,800
Was it true?

101
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,360
Girl,

102
00:05:50,280 --> 00:05:53,280
are you Zhu or Sun?

103
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,880
Zhu already died in Spain.

104
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:03,240
Only I'm left.

105
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:14,600
Why would your mom...

106
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:17,360
Why would she

107
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:19,040
do this to me?

108
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,520
Revenge.

109
00:06:27,937 --> 00:06:30,377
It's a revenge on the man
she once loved,

110
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:32,880
who stopped loving her.

111
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:57,720
It's my fault.

112
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:08,400
You acted so convincingly.

113
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:10,560
I almost believe you.

114
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:37,600
Lu Jiaming,

115
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:40,160
we've been together for twenty years.

116
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:42,120
Did you ever love me?

117
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:44,187
How could you do this to me?

118
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,850
What are you doing?

119
00:07:59,012 --> 00:08:00,172
I heard everything.

120
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:06,760
So

121
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:10,200
we're separating now, aren't we?

122
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:12,000
What are you talking about?

123
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:12,800
Those...

124
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,120
Those are two different things.

125
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:14,880
What are you saying?

126
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,560
We're separating now, aren't we?

127
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:19,320
Calm down.

128
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:20,160
Don't shout at me.

129
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:21,280
I'm already very annoyed.

130
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:23,120
So many things happened today.

131
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:26,400
Please calm down, okay?

132
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:29,840
Calm down?

133
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:32,200
Tell me.

134
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,280
Tell me!

135
00:08:37,920 --> 00:08:39,600
I never thought about leaving you.

136
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,960
You should try to understand me.

137
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,920
My Zhu...

138
00:08:43,800 --> 00:08:45,120
Zhu's gone, right?

139
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:47,280
What are you doing?

140
00:08:47,300 --> 00:08:48,240
You don't understand me at all.

141
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,000
And now you're making a scene here.

142
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:49,760
Are you crazy?

143
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:50,840
What's your problem?

144
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,400
I'm crazy? I have a problem?

145
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:52,760
Of course.

146
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:53,480
I'm crazy.

147
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,480
What are you trying to do?

148
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,640
There are so many things
happening in this family.

149
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:57,480
You've really gone mad.

150
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:04,400
I don't have the mood

151
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,640
or the patience

152
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:07,760
to listen to you making a fuss here.

153
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:09,000
I didn't know.

154
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:09,880
Making a fuss?

155
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:10,960
Of course you are.

156
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:12,760
So much has happened today.

157
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:13,640
Stop making trouble.

158
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:15,120
Don't act crazy, okay?

159
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,040
I...

160
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:17,200
I'm crazy?

161
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,720
I'm crazy?

162
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,400
I won't talk to you anymore.

163
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:23,760
I'll show you who's crazy.

164
00:09:24,160 --> 00:09:25,800
Come here.

165
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:27,440
What exactly are you trying to do?

166
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:30,360
Do you see this?

167
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:31,400
Do you see it?

168
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,800
These are Zhu's things.

169
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:37,280
Do you see them?

170
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,240
Don't touch her things.

171
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:40,600
Do you see them?

172
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:41,960
Don't touch her things!

173
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:43,720
You can't touch them, you know?

174
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:50,000
Zhu's gone.

175
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:50,800
Do you know?

176
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:53,480
You're not to touch them.

177
00:10:18,375 --> 00:10:22,875
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

178
00:10:23,100 --> 00:10:26,888
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

179
00:10:27,063 --> 00:10:31,138
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

180
00:10:31,138 --> 00:10:35,275
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

181
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:39,175
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

182
00:10:39,175 --> 00:10:42,950
♪I'll learn to stop longing for
what's gone♪

183
00:10:42,950 --> 00:10:45,225
♪The you in my memories♪

184
00:10:45,225 --> 00:10:47,238
♪Will fade from clarity♪

185
00:10:47,238 --> 00:10:52,675
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

186
00:10:54,238 --> 00:10:59,675
♪Forget you completely?♪
